Package: fb2ga
Type: Package
Title: A package that makes it very easy to extract Facebook ad data and then upload it to Google Analytics
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Randall Helms
Maintainer: Randall Helms <randall@neugelb.com>
Description: A couple of useful functions to move data from Facebook Ads to Google Analytics.
    Minimize your efforts! This package has functions to add UTM codes to any URL you want, extract data from your Facebook Ads account, format it, and then upload it to your Google Analytics account. The accompanying article contains all of the relevant information for how you can run through this process from start to finish.
